n style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;"><b>适合对象</b></span></font></div><div><p style="word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 'Microsoft yahei', 微软雅黑, 黑体, 'helvetica neue', 'lucida grande', helvetica, arial, sans-serif, 宋体; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); ">该课程设计为提供实践的精益知识和工具改进企业运营，同时帮助你在组织中启动精益改进项目。目标学员包括:</p><ul style="word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 'Microsoft yahei', 微软雅黑, 黑体, 'helvetica neue', 'lucida grande', helvetica, arial, sans-serif, 宋体; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); "><li style="word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; ">1.经理，工程师，主管，变革代理人，行政支持人员 ，非制造职能员工和主管</li><li style="word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; ">2.离散型生产企业，物流中心，建筑，服务，或多重流程工业</li></ul><div><font color="#444444" face="Microsoft yahei, 微软雅黑, 黑体, helvetica neue, lucida grande, helvetica, arial, sans-serif, 宋体"><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;"><br></span></font></div></div><div><font color="#444444" face="Microsoft yahei, 微软雅黑, 黑体, helvetica neue, lucida grande, helvetica, arial, sans-serif, 宋体"><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;"><b>实例赏析</b></span></font></div><div><p><a href="http://kicn.cn/data/attachment/portal/201210/12/115705ykll979eqh6nsjlk.png" target="_blank"><img src="http://kicn.cn/data/attachment/portal/201210/12/115705ykll979eqh6nsjlk.png"></a></p><p><a href="http://kicn.cn/data/attachment/portal/201210/12/115747yooflkke64hzj46d.png" target="_blank"><img src="http://kicn.cn/data/attachment/portal/201210/12/115747yooflkke64hzj46d.png"></a></p></div>";}}s:20:"custom_result_object";a:0:{}s:11:"current_row";i:0;s:8:"num_rows";i:20;s:8:"row_data";N;}